club.seedymusic.jpa.bean

Class Cd

  • java.lang.Object
    • club.seedymusic.jpa.bean.Cd

  • @Entity
public class Cd
extends java.lang.Object

    Cd Class

    This class is the entity bean used by the Java Persistence API. It represents a CD entry in the database.

    Version:
    Oct 9, 2017 Created this class.
    Author:
    Karim Sultan
